Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個時候我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.17,0:01:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那時奈砂她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天在茂下神社要舉辦祭典和煙花大會
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要不要也去游泳呢 典道君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道 快給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.37,0:03:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天可是上學的日子 別懶懶散散的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好煩啊 還沒好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早飯是昨晚的咖哩喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}接下來開始為您播報今日局地天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.33,0:03:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}有請茂下町的勝沼小姐——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}好的 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}其實我呢 現在來到了今晚將舉行煙花大會的茂下燈塔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}關於這邊的天氣呢 從上午開始就是晴朗的好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}下午至晚上預計天氣不會發生太大變化…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的啊 為什麼假期裡還有上學的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還算好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.22,0:04:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸媽媽下午不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你中午就隨便吃點冰箱裡的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要去哪裡嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}收集了一堆破爛說是要搞個跳蚤市場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在祭典這天?誰會去買啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她連店都不開了就非要去搞這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們剛剛說了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}孩子他爹 你不願意就算了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天賭點什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}輸了的傢伙就去性騷擾三浦老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.83,0:05:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}認真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}騎自行車不是佔優勢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有近道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 耍賴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給我等著典道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.95,0:05:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.09,0:05:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.69,0:06:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稔 你能來一個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.42,0:06:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你明明知道我來不了故意問的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞不好你也能表演一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}試試看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.14,0:07:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老師好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗨 早
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天也在搖動!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.35,0:07:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}D? E?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}F? G?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}H? I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}J?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.85,0:07:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}純一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}接得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}漂亮!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}可以準備進軍世界級了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}真的呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.50,0:08:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我從那裡跑了出來…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早上好奈砂 昨天說到的那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂可愛吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}及川嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪裡可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說我想向她表白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.09,0:08:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就去唄
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}暑假裡想兩個人一起去哪裡玩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.86,0:08:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比如說今天的煙花大會啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以說你去表白不就行了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼可能表白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果被拒絕了該怎麼辦啊 太丟人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰管你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:08:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天有在茂下神社舉行的的祭典和煙花大會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想必人會很多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和朋友一起去的人注意不要玩到太晚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.54,0:09:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老師你要和誰去呀?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和男朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.50,0:09:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}田島同學 你再不適可而止我就告你性騷擾了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我就用濫用職權告回去哦!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你啊 真的給我適可而止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.78,0:09:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 糟糕 過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 快下來 喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老師你得快點回去講課啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.96,0:09:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}趕快給大家講講神社的事啊 大家等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快點下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天打算怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛被學生問了「要和男朋友去嗎?」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.22,0:09:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎?這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能差不多該公開我們的關係了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別這樣啦 再說那個時候我們兩個人都喝醉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.57,0:10:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.88,0:10:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}及川同學 怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽讓我交給老師的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她要搬家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒?及川嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且說是就在暑假中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.11,0:10:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的假的?那還真是突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 她媽媽要再婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼說呢 這還真是不好說些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣好嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這不是打掃泳池的特權嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.08,0:11:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.37,0:11:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那傢伙也是負責打掃的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 只有我們倆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.15,0:11:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是游泳社的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.29,0:11:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天有社團活動嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.66,0:11:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去上個廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看到奈砂就想大便了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在說什麼胡話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}社團活動?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要游泳嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不游
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.63,0:12:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那為什麼…?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蜻蜓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:12:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}停在那兒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿掉牠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抓住牠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.47,0:13:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早上在海邊撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}石頭?玻璃嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.89,0:13:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道 感覺很漂亮就撿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒拉出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.81,0:14:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.68,0:14:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 我們來比50米游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.71,0:14:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}賭些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.09,0:14:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}賭什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.31,0:14:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那如果我贏了的話 給我買海賊王最新一期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你贏了呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我贏了的話…我就向奈砂表白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你耍賴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.72,0:14:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不想奈砂被搶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了?50米?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.16,0:14:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也要來!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是賭了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那如果我贏了 我說什麼你們都得答應
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:14:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.31,0:15:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那準備開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}預備
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安曇君 要去今天的煙花大會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們兩個人一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.90,0:16:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你問為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我五點去找你 要在家待著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛 腳踝狠狠地撞到泳池邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對了 誰贏了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.92,0:16:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個 是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是圓的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}扁的才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕對是圓的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們試想一下 那可是火藥爆炸啊 肯定是圓的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂喂 你們說煙花從側面看是圓的還是扁的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是什麼?煙花火箭?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是啊 是那種大的煙火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.01,0:17:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}扁的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別開玩笑了 肯定是圓的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.03,0:17:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}祐介覺得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.03,0:17:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.35,0:17:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且線香煙花不就是圓的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.40,0:17:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大型煙火又不一定嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼你們見過扁的煙花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.76,0:17:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我見過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:17:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.43,0:18:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稔說的話不能當真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去年在爺爺家看煙花大會的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.98,0:18:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從院子裡看就是扁的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.51,0:18:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爺爺還說從這邊看角度太不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看吧 爺爺都這麼說 肯定沒錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.55,0:18:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是爺爺糊塗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才沒有糊塗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼用多數表決決定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}根本不是這個問題啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.16,0:18:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}認為是扁的的人有哪些?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}我!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要這麼說我們就打個賭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}賭什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.80,0:18:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那如果煙花是扁的的話 你就把我們的暑假作業全做了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.33,0:18:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以可以 就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那如果是圓的怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給你三浦老師的內褲走光照片哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那種東西怎麼弄到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.35,0:18:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去照給你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.98,0:18:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼照?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不過 怎麼樣才能從側面看煙花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直升機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那很簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看好了 這個是茂下燈塔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}正好在海岸的側邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煙花是從這個茂下島燃放的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是說 從燈塔那邊就能側面看到煙花了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誰去看啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.77,0:19:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乾脆大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我也要去!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去吧去吧 這聽起來不是很有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.33,0:19:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 這樣暑假就可以隨便玩了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.38,0:19:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}隨便玩不了的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼辦好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.83,0:19:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去唄去唄 我們不是同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.85,0:19:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 那五點在茂下神社集合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 真的會拍內褲走光照片給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.38,0:20:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}超級期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就五點見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那傢伙為啥這麼情緒高漲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.95,0:20:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哇 嚇我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}噢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}噢什麼噢 為什麼你會在這
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你家也真是不注意安全 後門總是不鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.92,0:21:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你也別隨便進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有啥不行 反正你五點之前都閒著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好巧啊 我也閒著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是這個問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那瓶放了好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去好好打個招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哎呀 今天去學校了啊 很熱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.51,0:21:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我買了冰淇淋 大家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想吃哪個 奈砂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.17,0:21:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:21:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事沒事 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.97,0:22:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}學校那邊 手續辦完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.11,0:22:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}嗯 今天讓她告訴班主任了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.17,0:22:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}她和朋友分別 會很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.47,0:22:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}不 她朋友不多 不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}男朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}怎麼可能有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.10,0:22:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}誰知道呢 現在的年輕人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你賴皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好菜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.57,0:22:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 要五點了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.90,0:22:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稍微遲到一點也沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.47,0:22:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.90,0:22:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說 煙花一定是圓的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.11,0:22:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒? 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.45,0:22:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒?你是真的不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.44,0:22:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.00,0:22:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是傻瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.12,0:22:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管在哪個世界都不存在扁的煙花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.24,0:23:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為是火藥爆炸 所以不管從哪邊看肯定都是圓的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.39,0:23:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.66,0:23:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但萬一是扁的怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可能有那樣的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.98,0:23:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你為啥剛才不說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是配合一下那群傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.14,0:23:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.48,0:23:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 是扁的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.00,0:23:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.44,0:23:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼這副打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們不是要去冒險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.11,0:23:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.56,0:23:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊對了 和弘 煙花果然是扁的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.29,0:24:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這邊這位 實話告訴你 他可是在職的煙花工匠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煙花師都這麼說 肯定不會錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.24,0:24:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.23,0:24:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很痛 你輕一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.31,0:24:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哇 你還是去看一下醫生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.56,0:24:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒啥大不了的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是不懂啊 要是感染了破傷風可能會死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.80,0:24:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.70,0:24:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去我家找我爸給你看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.66,0:24:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}純一他們那邊我會轉告的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.17,0:24:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒 不要啊 一起去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.29,0:24:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會趕不上約定時間的 你趕緊去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.38,0:24:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.85,0:24:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我家見到奈砂的話 就告訴她我去不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.71,0:24:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.76,0:24:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為之前那傢伙邀請我去煙花大會
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.42,0:24:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.51,0:24:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.77,0:24:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛才啥時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.01,0:24:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在泳池的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.27,0:24:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟她去就好了啊 你喜歡她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.92,0:25:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊? 你說什麼 怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.69,0:25:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我什麼時候說過喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.43,0:25:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不是一直這麼說的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.52,0:25:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊? 怎麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.32,0:25:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}「喜歡她」「要去表白」這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.30,0:25:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玩笑啦 開玩笑的 我怎麼可能喜歡那種醜八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.98,0:25:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是傻瓜嗎 真是蠢得不行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.06,0:25:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.23,0:25:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請講
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.41,0:25:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}請問安曇君在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.93,0:25:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}祐介君嗎 好像還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.07,0:25:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能是去煙花大會了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.40,0:25:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.77,0:25:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個是在哪買的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.99,0:25:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.79,0:25:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.12,0:25:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒?典道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.78,0:25:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 他受了點傷 去我家找我爸看病了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.28,0:25:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就去你家接典道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.24,0:26:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.35,0:26:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.86,0:26:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和弘 你動作太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.51,0:26:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再來一杯燒酒蘇打
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.62,0:26:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你還不過去沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.47,0:26:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煙花大會準備好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.72,0:26:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且真的沒問題嗎 你那樣胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.88,0:26:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說煙花是扁的什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.58,0:26:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說過這話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.61,0:26:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.82,0:26:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 是祐介君介紹我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.30,0:26:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}破傷風?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.92,0:26:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種程度的小傷怎麼會感染破傷風
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.07,0:26:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}痛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.82,0:26:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要亂動哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.77,0:26:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼 祐介去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.60,0:27:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是去煙花大會了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.16,0:27:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 去什麼煙花大會
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.95,0:27:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一天就知道玩 所以我才想送他去私立學校
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.06,0:27:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個…煙花是圓的呢 還是扁的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.71,0:27:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.43,0:27:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我先去給你拿藥 請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.99,0:27:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.14,0:27:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在等祐介嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.16,0:27:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他不會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.68,0:27:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.29,0:28:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.29,0:28:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我邀請的是你 你會怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.54,0:28:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也會逃避嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.90,0:28:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是想著邀請自由泳比賽獲勝的那方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.68,0:28:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突然就想這麼做了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.12,0:28:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以為你會贏 可你為什麼輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.40,0:28:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為你游得太快了 我有點著急
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.96,0:28:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我的錯? 都是我的錯嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.65,0:29:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說起來 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.09,0:29:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.80,0:29:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.82,0:29:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你覺得是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.94,0:29:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.48,0:29:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我離家出走過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.30,0:29:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.46,0:29:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.76,0:29:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我要離開這個小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.21,0:29:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你開玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.11,0:29:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對 玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.98,0:29:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.41,0:29:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.70,0:30:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道為什麼我覺得你會贏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.01,0:30:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.68,0:30:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.28,0:30:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.48,0:30:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.02,0:30:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.34,0:30:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.46,0:30:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.39,0:30:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.20,0:30:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.68,0:31:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道君 幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.48,0:31:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要啊 我不想去 我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.62,0:31:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 那是怎麼回事 那是奈砂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.42,0:31:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.98,0:31:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看起來情況很糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.96,0:31:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她媽媽好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.51,0:31:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那傢伙怎麼回事 看起來問題很嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.62,0:31:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從來沒見過奈砂那副模樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.34,0:31:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.13,0:31:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那叫什麼來著?體罰?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.00,0:32:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}住手啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.68,0:32:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}給我走開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.26,0:32:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.84,0:32:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個時候 如果我…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.36,0:32:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我贏了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.32,0:32:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.21,0:32:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 典道 你這是要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.49,0:32:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.89,0:32:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.90,0:33:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了?50米?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.55,0:33:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也要來!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.50,0:33:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那如果我贏了 我說什麼你們都得答應
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.25,0:33:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.16,0:33:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.45,0:33:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}贏了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.12,0:33:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.14,0:34:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.34,0:34:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道君 要去今天的煙花大會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.35,0:34:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.26,0:34:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們兩個人一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.02,0:34:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.68,0:34:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你問為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.97,0:34:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.17,0:34:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我五點去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.35,0:34:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定要在家待著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.81,0:34:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}游到中途突然想大便
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.97,0:34:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.28,0:34:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是圓的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.20,0:34:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}扁的才對
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.58,0:34:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕對是圓的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.31,0:34:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們試想一下 那可是火藥爆炸啊 肯定是圓的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.96,0:34:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂喂 你們說煙花從側面看是圓的還是扁的?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.34,0:34:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是什麼?煙花火箭?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.62,0:34:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是啊 是那種大的煙火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.42,0:35:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}扁的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.78,0:35:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.81,0:35:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別開玩笑了 肯定是圓的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.65,0:35:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道覺得呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.50,0:35:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.95,0:35:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那麼你們見過扁的煙花嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.29,0:35:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我見過哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.53,0:35:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.09,0:35:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稔說的話不能當真啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.82,0:35:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.38,0:35:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去年在爺爺家看煙花大會的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.91,0:35:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從院子裡看就是扁的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.16,0:35:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爺爺還說從這邊看角度太不好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.41,0:35:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看吧 爺爺都這麼說 肯定沒錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.69,0:35:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 你要這麼說我們就打個賭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.51,0:35:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}OK
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.05,0:35:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}賭什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.35,0:35:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那如果煙花是扁的的話 你就把我們的暑假作業全做了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.00,0:35:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.39,0:36:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道你也會去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.31,0:36:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道 要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.03,0:36:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就五點見了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.54,0:37:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喲
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.68,0:37:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喲什麼喲 你怎麼進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.04,0:37:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你家也真是不注意安全 後門沒鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.57,0:37:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你也別隨便進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.74,0:37:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}學校那邊 手續辦完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.96,0:37:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}嗯 今天讓她告訴班主任了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.90,0:37:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}她和朋友分別 會很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.14,0:37:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}不 她朋友不多 不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.08,0:37:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}男朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.71,0:37:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}怎麼可能有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.92,0:37:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}誰知道呢 現在的年輕人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.04,0:37:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}及川嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.49,0:37:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可能去不了了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.03,0:37:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不小心和祐介他們約了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.44,0:37:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}兄弟之間的約定 可不能打破啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.77,0:38:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別去神社了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.76,0:38:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煙花什麼的 管他是圓的還是扁的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.99,0:38:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去海邊正常看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.77,0:38:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說 煙花一定是扁的啊 是吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.51,0:38:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒? 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.85,0:38:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.40,0:38:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼?你是真的不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.09,0:38:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 也許吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.57,0:38:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看 是這樣圓著爆炸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.70,0:38:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣從側面看起來 不就是扁的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.13,0:38:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.49,0:38:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以說 沒必要特地去燈塔看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.29,0:38:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就別去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.54,0:39:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就…不去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.50,0:39:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那瓶放了好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.44,0:39:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒?是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.09,0:39:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我去買點飲料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.73,0:39:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真的嗎 多謝了 我要碳酸飲料
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.48,0:39:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}OKOK
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.72,0:39:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.50,0:39:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}祐介在樓上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.01,0:39:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那怎麼辦 不去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.82,0:39:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.98,0:39:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.52,0:40:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道 果然還是去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.83,0:40:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我這就下樓 我們一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.99,0:40:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟大家約好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.03,0:40:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.52,0:40:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼辦?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.96,0:40:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上車
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.52,0:40:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}別管那麼多 快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.03,0:40:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂?怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.03,0:40:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這傢伙!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.94,0:40:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.25,0:41:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.87,0:41:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.96,0:41:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.22,0:41:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}來得好晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.57,0:41:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.47,0:41:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你幹嘛這麼生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.59,0:41:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我沒生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.77,0:42:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.68,0:42:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不去看煙花大會了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.51,0:42:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.45,0:42:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.83,0:42:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.92,0:42:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哎呀 不小心打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.05,0:42:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你說 我們去哪裡好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.86,0:42:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}東京?大阪?去哪裡都可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.05,0:42:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}離家出走?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.39,0:42:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是這樣的吧 你是離家出走了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.65,0:42:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是離家出走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.85,0:42:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.98,0:43:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私奔
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.02,0:43:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私奔?是指兩個人一起去死?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.88,0:43:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是殉情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.69,0:43:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好重 我們稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.72,0:43:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開什麼玩笑 不是你說要去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.14,0:43:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走不動了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.15,0:43:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}說起來 你到底在包裡裝了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.55,0:43:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你帶這些做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.89,0:43:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是打算去做旅行商人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.84,0:43:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你們再不快一點就趕不上了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.54,0:43:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那傢伙是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.32,0:43:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得女孩子啊 不管到哪裡都能找到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.32,0:43:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要謊報年齡說自己16歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.84,0:43:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看起來不像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.44,0:44:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.78,0:44:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說可以做什麼工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.15,0:44:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚上的工作啊 坐檯小姐 女調酒師什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.22,0:44:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.30,0:44:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼樣 看起來像是16歲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.23,0:45:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看這個 今早我在海邊撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.79,0:45:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.19,0:45:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.00,0:45:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是不知為何 當我發現它時我就決定出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.71,0:45:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.96,0:45:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道君要是贏了…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.35,0:45:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯 我下定了決心要是你贏了自由泳比賽我就出走
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.43,0:45:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒錯 所以你要對我負責啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.84,0:45:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你願意和我一起走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.69,0:45:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.06,0:45:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}住手
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.64,0:46:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放開我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.13,0:46:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.84,0:46:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要 典道君 幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.38,0:46:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.22,0:46:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}放開我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.86,0:46:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 幫幫我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.62,0:46:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道君 典道君
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.09,0:46:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道君 典道君!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.41,0:46:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.65,0:47:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.40,0:47:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.42,0:47:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道君!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.54,0:47:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那時候如果我…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.04,0:47:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我和奈砂上了電車
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.30,0:48:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.58,0:48:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.18,0:48:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是典道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.70,0:48:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.61,0:48:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你為什麼沒來神社會合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.49,0:48:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 稍微有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.53,0:48:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以事情辦完你就來追我們了?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.33,0:48:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.88,0:48:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那好吧 那就一起去燈塔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.54,0:48:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說關於煙花是圓的還是扁的 我已經沒啥興趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.30,0:48:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.31,0:48:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開什麼玩笑 我們是為了什麼才走到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.13,0:49:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.00,0:49:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.40,0:49:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說她為什麼要來你家
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.88,0:49:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 是因為在泳池的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.11,0:49:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.63,0:49:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也說不太清楚…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.10,0:49:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你們在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.70,0:49:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.20,0:49:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.18,0:49:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.76,0:49:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.50,0:50:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.90,0:50:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底怎麼樣 煙花是圓的還是扁的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.05,0:50:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還沒開始放呢 反正煙花也肯定是圓的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.09,0:50:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是是扁的 你真的要把作業全部做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.63,0:50:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡的門開著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.35,0:50:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哇 好厲害 這可以爬上去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.69,0:50:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}乾脆去上面看怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.57,0:50:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好啊 上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.00,0:50:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還沒到頂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.10,0:50:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樓梯真長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.01,0:50:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}開始放了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.09,0:50:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.15,0:50:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都說了肯定是圓的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.20,0:50:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}暑假結束我就去表白
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.70,0:50:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第二學期一開始 我一定要告訴奈砂我喜歡她
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.62,0:51:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好窄
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.62,0:51:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快點
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.57,0:51:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快點
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.26,0:51:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喔 好高
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.85,0:51:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.89,0:51:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}圓的還是扁的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.74,0:51:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看吧 是扁的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.21,0:51:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.79,0:51:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.45,0:51:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爺爺謝謝你!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.44,0:51:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}全部的作業交給你了!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.06,0:51:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.93,0:51:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.46,0:51:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太棒了 太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.21,0:51:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.68,0:51:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}贏得太容易
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.21,0:51:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煙花不可能是扁的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.20,0:52:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說 煙花一定是圓的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.18,0:52:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒? 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.83,0:52:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.69,0:52:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒?你是真的不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.33,0:52:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.52,0:52:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是傻瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.50,0:52:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管在哪個世界都不存在扁的煙花啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.93,0:52:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為是火藥爆炸 所以不管從哪邊看肯定都是圓的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.89,0:52:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.67,0:52:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但萬一是扁的怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.98,0:52:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不可能有那樣的世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.95,0:52:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.37,0:52:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這種事不可能發生的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.37,0:52:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}祐介
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.46,0:52:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}由我來奪回奈砂
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.19,0:53:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我和奈砂上了電車…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.00,0:53:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我覺得女孩子啊 不管到哪裡都能找到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.18,0:53:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要說自己16歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.31,0:53:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼樣 看起來像是16歲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.26,0:53:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是今早我在海邊撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.02,0:53:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.55,0:53:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我決定了…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.54,0:53:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道君贏了自由泳比賽我就決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.71,0:53:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}決定離家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.41,0:53:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以你要對我負責啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.26,0:53:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.34,0:53:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}對·我·負·責
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.27,0:54:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒??
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.48,0:54:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你願意和我一起走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.45,0:54:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.28,0:54:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.97,0:54:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.81,0:54:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.16,0:54:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快走
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.19,0:54:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.42,0:55:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.62,0:55:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剛剛真是開心
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.39,0:55:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你很厲害啊 典道君 你打架很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.97,0:55:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我對你刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.78,0:55:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊不…我也不知道哪裡來的氣勢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.92,0:55:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說那人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.17,0:55:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我媽媽要再婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.77,0:55:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很厲害吧 這是她第三次結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.19,0:56:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她第一次結婚時的出軌對象就是我的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.32,0:56:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是後來懷上了我 兩個人就私奔到了這個小鎮
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.29,0:56:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她說簡直就像電視劇或者電影一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.81,0:56:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我是私奔夫婦的女兒 很酷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.22,0:56:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是爸爸已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.80,0:56:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爸爸去世才過了一年 媽媽又和新的男人在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.45,0:57:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.91,0:57:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以你才想離家出走嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.36,0:57:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已經在離家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.43,0:57:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說能別再用離家出走這個幼稚的詞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.52,0:57:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這·叫·私·奔
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.91,0:57:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這可是叫私奔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.41,0:57:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為我隨了我媽媽碧池的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.09,0:57:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下來怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.72,0:57:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們兩個人去東京生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.20,0:57:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是不能當陪酒的話 該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.94,0:57:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}進軍演藝圈怎麼樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.10,0:57:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要去做偶像啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.46,0:57:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行嗎 我覺得我挺適合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.25,0:57:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哎? 這是什麼歌
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.66,0:58:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是我媽媽經常在卡拉OK唱的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.74,0:58:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是松田聖子這個人唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.66,0:58:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}從小經常聽 就記住了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.52,1:00:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其實我明白
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.11,1:00:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}離家出走是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.81,1:00:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}私奔也是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.03,1:00:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是在就這樣轉學之前
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.00,1:00:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就今天一天 能和典道君在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.17,1:00:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦? 安曇君
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.15,1:00:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.47,1:00:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}糟了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.84,1:00:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒? 剛剛是典道?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.22,1:00:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂也在對吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.12,1:01:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼回事 祐介
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.72,1:01:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼他們兩個在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.12,1:01:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是不是在交往
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.87,1:01:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可惡
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.88,1:01:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 等等 要去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.01,1:01:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.96,1:01:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等下
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.31,1:01:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}暴露了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.00,1:01:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和你在一起被看到了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.40,1:01:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為什麼 不能暴露嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.59,1:01:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 不 也不是
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.89,1:01:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因為祐介喜歡你…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.04,1:01:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.55,1:01:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他們追上來了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.09,1:01:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.71,1:01:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂 等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.07,1:01:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哇 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.39,1:01:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.80,1:02:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下車吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.41,1:02:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下一站下車
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.97,1:02:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂
Dialogue: 0,1:02:11.12,1:02:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這邊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.70,1:02:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道 到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.11,1:02:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.35,1:02:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跳吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.21,1:03:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 我們要去哪兒
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.71,1:03:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.52,1:03:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.68,1:03:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.39,1:03:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.76,1:03:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.57,1:03:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你之後不在了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.69,1:03:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少今天我想和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.56,1:03:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.03,1:03:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}島田同學 及川同學?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.92,1:03:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚上好
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.28,1:03:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}晚上好
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.17,1:03:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然在交往嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.81,1:03:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.53,1:03:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等下啦
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.16,1:03:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我說 你們在做什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.72,1:03:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們在研究煙花是扁的還是圓的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.70,1:03:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啥?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.03,1:03:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.38,1:04:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什麼啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.16,1:04:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}誒?晴子的胸部本來是這樣又小又平的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.58,1:04:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}幹什麼啊 變態
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.11,1:04:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吶 典道君
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.76,1:04:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煙花是圓的呢?還是扁的呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.04,1:04:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天你們不是在教室討論嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.36,1:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}當然是圓的了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.04,1:04:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是嗎?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.52,1:04:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}絕對是的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.31,1:05:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.17,1:05:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是什麼 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,1:05:27.51,1:05:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.45,1:05:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對 這個世界不對
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.70,1:05:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪裡不對
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.79,1:05:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}煙花不會是這種形狀的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.12,1:05:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是什麼形狀都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.39,1:05:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管是圓形還是扁狀 還是這種奇怪的形狀
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.65,1:05:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要能和典道君在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.05,1:05:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那種事情都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.83,1:06:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找到了!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.71,1:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道 你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.92,1:06:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}入口在哪裡來著
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.00,1:06:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這邊這邊 快點
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.29,1:06:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}奈砂 奈砂 快下來
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.53,1:06:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.44,1:06:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果…
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.87,1:06:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果沒有被祐介還有你的媽媽發現的話
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.78,1:06:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們兩個能一直在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.84,1:06:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要扔出去了
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.61,1:06:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}典道
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.40,1:06:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.71,1:07:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們兩個人去東京生活吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.62,1:07:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦?
Dialogue: 0,1: